
Webradio using open source technologies and models, and treating open source topics as well.

URL = http://freematrix.us/radio/schedule 

"Freematrix Radio is an online streaming radio station based on the open Ogg Vorbis and Icecast technologies. We play content content that is either Creative Commons, Public Domain, or has been licensed to us by it's authors for Royalty-Free Play. Completely volunteer-run and powered by bandwidth and server donations, we act professional but we make sure we have fun."

